@freshonline There's an open issue (#721) about running migrations with geth `1.8.0-stable`.

Could you try downgrading to `1.7.3` and see if that helps? There may be additional issues you're facing but `1.8.0` is known to be unusable at the moment. We're actively investigating the cause the and will hopefully fix this in next patch release. 

Closing as duplicate of #721
